Subject: Basic Silicone Molding and Resin Casting Techniques
Description: Learn how to make a simple silicone block mold and then cast your very own small sculpture (dragon, cat, or penguin) to take with you! Silicone types and resin types will be discussed as well as troubleshooting. Please sign up in advance at Ops.   Speakers include:Melissa Ebbe - Track: DIY  - Duration: 1 hour and 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
